What is CroSKull

Bonesville has always been a mysterious town. Among the dark streets of the city, it is rare to see people stopping to talk to each other. Many elderly people leave their homes just to carry out duties or run errands, whereas the few children who have never played with each other do not know what fun is. At Bonesville, everything is sad, gloomy, melancholic, still. Just one person’s soul stands out across all the grey souls of the city… Dr. Jiko spends most of his time in his secret laboratory located inside the dark Bonesville Castle. After years of failure, he managed to improve his alchemical formula By combining mysterious potions, he found a way to bring joy and life back to the city… 6,666 funny and crazy Croskulls are ready to invade the streets!
The Croskull is a collection of 6,666 uniquely generated NFTs stored in the Cronos Chain. Each Croskull NFT is based on 6 attributes with different rarities. A Croskull is not simply a PFP but is also the key to the insane Dr. Jiko’s laboratory experiments.

What We Have

Tavern

You can handle your croskull, can send them in Adventure, write their story, look at your inventory and even sell them.

Adventure

Sending a croskull in adventure allows you to earn Grave and Soul. You can see how much wealth are ready to be claimed, but watch out, if you retire earlier the skull won't be happy!

Marketplace

This is a magic portal connected with Ebisu's Bay. You can look for a new croskull or for one of the 666 mystery potions dropped by DR Jiko and buy it!

Merchant

A new merchant appears near Bonesville: noone knows who he is or where he comes from, the only thing we know is that if he has enough coins he will bring new merch.

Raffle

Bonesville is famous for its raffle with great prizes. Join our raffle, the only thing you need is a bunch of Graves! BUT be careful DR. Jiko creates his own raffle, the crazy raffle. Don't miss out!

Bank

The Bank lets you help Bonesville to be built. You can lock your Grave for a period of time to help build a house and receive Rude or use your Grave to earn more Graves.
